' RELATIONSHIPS
' ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

' Pipeline wiring
IngestionController --> IngestionPipeline
IngestionController --> TrackingService
IngestionController --> IngestionJobStore
IngestionController --> IngestionJobRepository
IngestionPipeline <|.. DefaultIngestionPipeline
DefaultIngestionPipeline --> IngestionJobStore
DefaultIngestionPipeline --> SourceHandler
DefaultIngestionPipeline --> DownloadStrategy
DefaultIngestionPipeline --> ProcessingStrategy
DefaultIngestionPipeline --> IngestionRepository

' Strategy implementations
DownloadStrategy <|.. YtDlpDownloadStrategy
DownloadStrategy <|.. Aria2DownloadStrategy
Aria2DownloadStrategy --> IngestionJobStore : registers GID
ProcessingStrategy <|.. ExtractionProcessingStrategy
ProcessingStrategy <|.. FfmpegProcessingStrategy

' FfmpegProcessingStrategy dependencies
FfmpegProcessingStrategy --> TmdbMediaEnrichmentService
FfmpegProcessingStrategy --> MediaInfoService

' Enrichment
TmdbMediaEnrichmentService <|.. TmdbMediaEnrichmentServiceImpl
TmdbMediaEnrichmentServiceImpl --> RecordEntity : loads via RecordRepository
TmdbMediaEnrichmentServiceImpl --> TvSeriesTmdbEntity : resolves episode
TvSeriesTmdbEntity --> SeasonEntity
SeasonEntity --> EpisodeEntity
RecordEntity --> TmdbEntity
TmdbEntity <|-- MovieTmdbEntity
TmdbEntity <|-- TvSeriesTmdbEntity

' MediaInfo
MediaInfoService <|.. MediaInfoServiceImpl
MediaInfoController --> MediaInfoService
MediaInfoServiceImpl --> MediaFileRepository
MediaInfoServiceImpl --> MediaFileEntity

' Entities
MediaFileEntity --> TrackEntity : tracks (OneToMany)
TrackEntity <|-- GeneralTrackEntity
TrackEntity <|-- VideoTrackEntity
TrackEntity <|-- AudioTrackEntity
TrackEntity <|-- TextTrackEntity
TrackEntity <|-- ImageTrackEntity
MediaFileEntity --> RecordEntity : record (ManyToOne)

' Persistence
IngestionRepository <|.. NoOpIngestionRepository
IngestionRepository <|.. JpaIngestionRepository
JpaIngestionRepository --> IngestionJobRepository
IngestionJobRepository --> DB_JOBS
MediaFileRepository --> DB_FILES
MediaFileEntity ..> DB_FILES
TrackEntity ..> DB_TRACKS

' ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
' SEQUENCE: GID Tracking for Aria2 Pause / Resume
' ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
legend right
  **GID Tracking Flow (Aria2)**
  ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  1. POST /api/ingestion  →  pipeline.start(request)
  2. DefaultIngestionPipeline  →  jobStore.register(jobId, request)
  3. Aria2DownloadStrategy  →  aria2Rpc.addUri(url)  →  GID returned
  4. Aria2DownloadStrategy  →  jobStore.setGid(jobId, gid)
  5. Aria2DownloadStrategy  →  jobStore.setCancelAction(jobId, fn)
  6. PUT /{jobId}/pause  →  controller reads jobStore.getGid(jobId)
                          →  aria2Rpc.pause(gid)
  7. PUT /{jobId}/resume →  aria2Rpc.unpause(gid)
                          →  poll loop resumes automatically
  8. YOUTUBE jobs:  pause/resume return HTTP 400
  ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  **TMDB Enrichment Flow (FfmpegProcessingStrategy)**
  ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  1. Move temp file → final directory
  2. enrichmentService.enrich(file, recordId, season, ep, jobId)
       a. Load RecordEntity → TmdbEntity
       b. If TV: resolve EpisodeEntity (still image path, ep name)
       c. Download poster/still from TMDB CDN (HttpClient)
       d. FFmpeg: embed poster as attached_pic, set metadata title
       e. Rename: Title.SXXEXX.EpName.ext (TV) / name_enriched.ext (movie)
       f. Delete original + temp poster
  3. mediaInfoService.collectAndPersist(enrichedFile, recordId, jobId)
       a. Run: mediainfo --output=JSON {path}
       b. Parse JSON → MediaFileEntity + TrackEntity hierarchy
       c. Persist to media_files + media_tracks tables
  ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  **Enum Columns (all stored as VARCHAR via @Enumerated(STRING))**
    MirrorStatus   : QUEUED | STARTED | DOWNLOADING | PAUSED |
                     PROCESSING | SUCCESS | FAILED | CANCELLED
    PipelineStepType: SOURCE_RESOLUTION | DOWNLOAD | EXTRACTION |
                      PROCESSING | COMPLETE
    SourceType     : YOUTUBE | HTTP | TORRENT | UNKNOWN
  ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  **Single-Table Inheritance (media_tracks)**
    track_type discriminator values:
      General | Video | Audio | Text | Image
    All 5 subtypes share one table; unused columns are NULL
    extraJson (MySQL JSON) stores full raw MediaInfo output
    ImageTrackEntity.source: EMBEDDED (found in file) | TMDB (added by enrichment)
end legend

@enduml
